  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p757570/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201511/8503944209d44b788bd766798b7a37aa.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tThe joy of sleeping with a beautiful partner &mdash; and we mean the sleeping part &mdash; is something many of us don&rsquo;t get to experience on a regular enough basis.和漂亮的伴侣共眠的乐趣<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size: large; line-height: 27px; text-align: center;\">&mdash;&mdash;</span>指的是睡觉本身，并不是我们多数人可以常常经历的。</p>\n<p>\n\tBut what about the ladies? Do they get to enjoy the wonders of sleeping next to a hot guy enough in their busy lives? It seems the answer is yes, since there is a job called a soine-shi &mdash; a professional snuggler.那女性呢？生活繁忙，她们是不是也企盼与火辣的帅哥同眠呢？答案似乎是肯定的，因为现在就有个叫作soine-shi的工作，即&ldquo;职业陪睡师&rdquo;。</p>\n<p>\n\tOne such ikemen &ldquo;hunk&rdquo; version of this little-known trade is Kaede Ichijo, a 24-year-old snuggler who visits the apartments of Japanese girls in their thirties to help &ldquo;heal&rdquo; them through enjoying a drink together. And then they lie down on the futon for some one-on-one shuteye time.这一行当鲜为人知，现年24岁的小帅哥Kaede Ichijo便是此行的&ldquo;型男&rdquo;陪睡师，他造访三十几岁的日本女生，与她们同饮，帮她们&ldquo;疗伤&rdquo;。尔后，他们叠躺在一起共眠。</p>\n<p>\n\tThere&rsquo;s no &ldquo;extras&rdquo; but Kaede Ichijo offers the client his arm, and she snuggles up to him for some rest. Kaede Ichijo joined the &ldquo;snuggle industry&rdquo; and now has around 10 regular clients &mdash; all women in their thirties and forties. In total he has offered sleeping services for 300 women.但没有&ldquo;其它额外&rdquo;的服务了， 不过Kaede Ichijo会伸出臂膀，让客户蜷缩在旁休憩。Kaede Ichijo加入了&ldquo;依偎产业&rdquo;，现在约摸有10来个固定客户&mdash;&mdash;都是三四十多岁的女性。他总共为300名女性提供了睡眠服务。</p>\n<p>\n\tA daytime nap course costs from &yen;20,000 (around $160) for 2 hours, or a full six-hour &ldquo;goodnight&rdquo; course is from &yen;50,000 (over $400). You can even hire such soine-shi to come visit you in a love hotel for some mutual shuteye.白天小睡价在两小时两万日元（约160美元），整晚六小时&ldquo;安睡&rdquo;价是5万日元（超过400美元），你甚至可以雇佣陪睡师去情侣酒店共眠共枕。</p>\n<p>\n\tThere is a growing trend for this kind of service: the Ikemeso Danshi service recently started, offering &ldquo;dispatch&rdquo; men sent out to offices to give kabe-don for crying girls.这样的业务日趋流行，最近 Ikemeso Danshi服务开业了，&rdquo;派遣&ldquo;男士去办公室&ldquo;壁咚&rdquo;，安抚哭哭啼啼的女生。</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #999999;\">\n\t声明：本双语文章的中文翻译系沪江英语原创内容，转载请注明出处。中文翻译仅代表译者个人观点，仅供参考。如有不妥之处，欢迎指正。</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #999999;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201511/333bbd72e5bd435eb2903f707d570812.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/166578801072/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>【</strong><strong>12.12</strong></a><strong><a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/166578801072/\" target=\"_blank\">学习趴】</a>职场节目单：（优惠惊喜大放送！）</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/15199006/intro/?source=16549\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">沪江口语生活系列L1-L3【外教1V1 全额奖学金班】</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/lesson/p3_1425759/try?source=16554\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201511/0993c7eb-bca8-446f-89ce-9bc1d14f07ac.png\" style=\"border-style: none; display: inline;\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/15199006/intro/?source=16549\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"23\" src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201511/e4875b06-3bfa-41be-abe6-a8ab53984828.png\" style=\"border-style: none; display: inline;\" title=\"\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"60\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/15199006/intro/?source=16549\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">沪江口语生活系列L1-L5【外教1V1 全额奖学金班】</a>&nb